                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.512/586.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">International Development
                            Company</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Los Angeles</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-03-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 25, 1915</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Own in Lower California, Mexico, forty valuable iron properties, held twenty-five
                    years. Local dictator demands payment taxes American money. This, and previous
                    illegal double tax, makes amount ten times legally due. Other factions refuse
                    recognition payment. Formally protest. Request advice what action pursue. Kindly
                    wire collect. Time expires first.</p>
                <closer>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">The International Development Company.</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
